  <brief_title>NSAIDs Treatment in Children With Pleuropneumonia</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Role of Non Steroidal Anti Inflammatory Drugs in the Treatment of Pleuropneumonia in Children. a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
