  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the influence of routine NSAIDs treatment for
      hospitalized children with pleuropneumonia in comparison with acetominophen treatment (all in
      conjunction with adequate antibiotic therapy).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
